<section class="row-col fullsize">
	<div class="center-box">
		<div class="part-1">
			<h1 id='title'>About</h1>
			<p>
				Hey all, I am JJ, an upcoming front-end developer living in Berlin, Germany
				who loves drawing and building websites. 
				On this page you can see my very first personal web project <i>Dusk</i>.
				<i>Dusk</i> is a comic project started by myself in 2015, which combines modern web technologies
				with my comic art, finally creating an innovative experience of comic reading.
				The story for <i>Dusk</i> has been on my mind for some years already, but now finally
				finds its way to curious readers.			
			</p>
			<p><img src="#" alt="Image for about us"/></p>
			<h2 class="mt-2">About the story of Dusk</h2>
			<p>
				<i>Dusk</i> tells the story of a young graduate student who one day accidentally discovers another
				world which is very different from our own. Describing his journey through this world, meeting 
				new characters and hopefully finding his way back home is the main plot of this story. 
			</p>
			<h2 class="mt-2">About the web technologies</h2>
			<p>
				This page you are reading <i>Dusk</i> on, is built upon the innovative MVC framework <a href="http://emberjs.com/"
				target="ember" class="link">Ember.js</a>
				using the command line tool <a href="http://www.ember-cli.com/" target="embercli" class="link">Ember-CLI</a>. 
				The ongoing modernization of web design and programming languages
				made the implemenation of a big amount of animations, sliders and other fancy elements on this site possible
				using mostly <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/HTML5" target="htmlfive" class="link">HTML5</a>
				and <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS3" target="cssthree" class="link">CSS3</a> techniques. 
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
